pull.body:
Removes the redudant wallet reference from `WalletImpl`.

```cpp
// before:
std::shared_ptr<CWallet> m_shared_wallet;
CWallet& m_wallet;

// after
std::shared_ptr<CWallet> m_wallet;
```

